Gareth Yuen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gareth_Yuen 0 Gareth Yuen is an Australian actor who portrays the character Dax Lo, the Blue Ranger on the 2007 television series Power Rangers: Operation Overdrive. He appeared at the Power Morphicon in June 2007. He is a graduate of Sydney's National Institute of Dramatic Art (NIDA).
